{"tid":2276910,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"依家並非邊個做總統既問題；而係守護我地爭取既公義！","createTime":"2020-11-08T06:09:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T06:09:23.000Z","uid":109345,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c2bf61a01218fe0b65c5717e0178f3f21bb1d185","tid":2276910,"uid":109345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T06:09:23.000Z","msg":"事實上，無論你是否支持Trump，依家都唔應該接受目前既選舉結果。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n千祈唔好被傳媒講多幾次就信，大話講100次就會有人信，就唔會再有人追求真理。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要留意返，已經有幾個states進入司法程序，特朗普團隊已經開展一系列法律行動，係未有最後legitimate official results之前，大家唔好當拜登當選，一切未有塵埃落定。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n傳媒既報道，只會形成社會壓力，令到更多人接受依家個結果，呢個可能係民主黨最大既企圖。<br />\n但係 No One is above the LAW<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有人話要轉態支持拜登，要重新規劃國際路線。我唔想做墻頭草，更加唔想為爭取公義卻放棄公義、放棄相信法治。<br />\n<br />\n以下疑點暫時未有任何有說服力答案，點解要接受依家所謂既結果？如果接受，是否已經成為了對抗法治公義既幫凶？放棄去尋求真正答案？<br />\n1. 點不完的票數(僅適用於拜登落後時)<br />\n2. 驚人90%投票率<br />\n3. 死人票<br />\n4. 遺失選票<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/108970510452155/posts/382389939776876/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F108970510452155%2Fposts%2F382389939776876%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=ltJnWG3kir489%2BLnRwft25q%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=36e856a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/108970510452155/posts/382389939776876/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n日本手足都未放棄， 我地依家認拜登係總統？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/shujamtaro/status/1325271909743865857?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fshujamtaro%2Fstatus%2F1325271909743865857%3Fs%3D20&d=ltJnWG3kir489%2BLnRwft25q%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=674645b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fshujamtaro%2Fstatus%2F1325271909743865857%3Fs%3D20&h=7241aada\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/shujamtaro/status/1325271909743865857?s=20</a><br />\n#StoptheSteal<br />\n#LetTheCourtDecides<br />\n<br />\n假如最後出曬證據真係拜登得到所有legal votes而勝出，再探討之後既抗爭路線也不遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}